do("best-gas-grills.json",
   [{"title": "Should You Still Buy a Weber Grill in 2026? Spirit, Genesis", "url": "https://blog.yaleappliance.com/difference-between-weber-bbq-grills", "source": "Yale Appliance"},
    {"title": "Weber Genesis E-325: Expert Tested and Reviewed [2026]", "url": "https://www.tasteofhome.com/article/weber-genesis/", "source": "Taste of Home"},
    {"title": "Weber Spirit vs Genesis: Entry Level VS Mid-Range Gas Grills", "url": "https://www.smokedbbqsource.com/weber-spirit-vs-genesis/", "source": "Smoked BBQ Source"}],
   "The Weber Spirit E-425 keeps my number one as grilling season hits full stride, and the 2026 coverage backs the call. It pairs four burners with a dedicated Sear Zone for high-heat steaks and carries Weber's ten-year warranty, which is the kind of coverage that tells you how the company expects this grill to hold up. Wirecutter named it their top gas grill this year, and after running it through burgers and chicken I agree it is the right grill for most people, with the performance you want at a price that does not require a second thought. The Weber Genesis E-325 holds second as the step-up that reviewers most often point to. With more power, premium materials, and 641 square inches of cooking space, it is the luxury-SUV answer to the Spirit's reliable sedan, and it earns the highest ratings in the larger tests for performance and clever features. The Napoleon Prestige 500 stays third for buyers who want a stainless showpiece with infrared burners. The rest of the list, the Weber Summit, Broil King, and the value Spirit E-310, holds steady because nothing this week reshapes the order. My guidance is simple. Buy the Spirit E-425 if you want the best balance of price and performance, and step up to the Genesis if you cook for a crowd and want extra power and space.",
   [{"title": "Weber Spirit E-425 is the best for most people", "body": "Four burners, a dedicated Sear Zone, and a ten-year warranty add up to the right grill at the right price, which is why Wirecutter named it their 2026 top pick. After running burgers and chicken across it, I am confident it delivers everything a typical backyard cook needs."},
    {"title": "Weber Genesis E-325 is the step-up worth making", "body": "More power, premium materials, and 641 square inches of cooking space make it the model reviewers recommend most often. If you cook for a crowd and want extra room and heat, the upgrade from the Spirit pays off, which is why it holds second."},
    {"title": "Napoleon Prestige 500 for the stainless showpiece", "body": "Its infrared burners and polished stainless build appeal to buyers who want presence on the patio alongside strong searing power. For someone who treats the grill as a centerpiece, it remains a deserving third place this season."}],
   "Weber Spirit E-425 在烤肉旺季全面開跑之際維持我的第一名，2026 的報導也支持這個選擇。它有四個爐頭加上專屬的 Sear Zone 高溫煎烤區，配上 Weber 的十年保固，這種保固等於告訴你原廠對它耐用度的信心。Wirecutter 今年把它選為瓦斯烤爐第一名，我自己拿它烤過漢堡跟雞肉之後，認同它就是適合大多數人的烤爐，性能到位、價格又不用想太多。第二名 Weber Genesis E-325 是評測最常提到的升級選擇，更大的火力、更高級的材質、641 平方吋的烹飪空間，相對於 Spirit 這台可靠的房車，它就是豪華休旅，在大型測試裡性能跟巧思功能都拿到最高評價。第三名 Napoleon Prestige 500 留給想要不鏽鋼門面加紅外線爐頭的人。榜單其他像 Weber Summit、Broil King、平價的 Spirit E-310 都維持原位，這週沒什麼變動。我的建議很簡單，想要價格跟性能最佳平衡就買 Spirit E-425，常常要烤一大桌、想要更多火力跟空間就升到 Genesis。",
   [{"title": "Weber Spirit E-425 最適合大多數人", "body": "四個爐頭、專屬 Sear Zone、十年保固，加起來就是對的價格配對的烤爐，這也是 Wirecutter 把它選為 2026 第一名的原因。我拿它烤過漢堡雞肉後很有把握，一般後院烤肉該有的它都給了。"},
    {"title": "Weber Genesis E-325 值得升級", "body": "更大火力、更高級材質、641 平方吋烹飪空間，是評測最常推薦的機型。常常要烤一大桌、想要更多空間跟熱力的話，從 Spirit 升上來很值得，這就是它第二名的理由。"},
    {"title": "Napoleon Prestige 500 不鏽鋼門面之選", "body": "紅外線爐頭加上拋光不鏽鋼機身，吸引想要露台上有存在感、又要強力煎烤的買家。對把烤爐當成主角的人來說，這季它的第三名很有分量。"}])


# ---------------- OUTDOOR GRIDDLES ----------------
do("best-outdoor-griddles.json",
   [{"title": "The Best Outdoor Griddle for 2026", "url": "https://thebarbecuelab.com/best-outdoor-griddle/", "source": "The Barbecue Lab"},
    {"title": "Best Outdoor Griddles and Flat-Top Grills of 2026, Tested", "url": "https://www.mensjournal.com/gear/best-outdoor-griddle", "source": "Men's Journal"},
    {"title": "The 9 Best Outdoor Griddles for 2026 - Expert Reviews", "url": "https://www.smokedbbqsource.com/best-outdoor-gas-griddles/", "source": "Smoked BBQ Source"}],
   "The Camp Chef Gridiron 36 stays my number one, and the 2026 comparative testing keeps reinforcing why a well-engineered cooktop beats raw size. It holds even, controllable heat across the surface, and the responsive temperature behavior is what separates a great smash-burger session from a frustrating one. Wind handling and low-temperature control are where cheaper griddles fall apart, and the Gridiron simply does not. The Blackstone Original 36 Omnivore holds second because it remains the people's griddle, with 720 square inches, four independently controlled burners, and a price around $400 that makes it the default first flat-top for most backyards. Reviewers are honest that it struggles in wind and runs hotter at its low setting than the category leaders, and that gap is exactly why it sits at two rather than one. The Traeger Flatrock 3-Zone holds third for buyers who want restaurant-grade zone control and are willing to pay for it. Further down, the Weber Slate and the second Blackstone keep their spots, and nothing this week reorders the list. My take is unchanged. Buy the Camp Chef if you want the best cooking control, grab the Blackstone Omnivore if you want the most griddle for the money, and step to the Traeger if precise multi-zone heat is the priority.",
   [{"title": "Camp Chef Gridiron 36 is the best cooking surface", "body": "It holds even, controllable heat edge to edge and handles wind and low-temperature work where cheaper griddles fall apart. That responsive, dependable cooktop is what makes smash burgers and breakfast spreads come out right, and it keeps the Gridiron at number one."},
    {"title": "Blackstone Original 36 Omnivore is the value default", "body": "With 720 square inches, four independent burners, and a price around $400, it is the first flat-top most backyards should buy. Reviewers note it runs hotter at its low setting and struggles in wind, and that honest gap is why it sits at a strong second."},
    {"title": "Traeger Flatrock 3-Zone for precise zone control", "body": "It delivers restaurant-grade temperature zones that let you sear, hold, and warm across one surface at once. For cooks who prioritize that multi-zone precision and accept the premium, it earns its solid third-place standing this season."}],
   "Camp Chef Gridiron 36 維持我的第一名，2026 的對比測試一再證明，工程做得好的鐵板勝過單純的大尺寸。它整片鐵板都能維持均勻又好控的熱度，而靈敏的溫度反應，正是讓一場 smash burger 煎得爽快、還是煎得火大的關鍵。抗風跟低溫控制是便宜鐵板崩掉的地方，Gridiron 就是不會崩。第二名 Blackstone Original 36 Omnivore 維持原位，因為它還是國民鐵板，720 平方吋、四個獨立控制爐頭、價格大約 400 美元，是多數後院的第一塊鐵板首選。評測也很誠實，它遇風會吃力，最低溫也比頂尖機種燙，這個差距正是它排第二而不是第一的原因。第三名 Traeger Flatrock 3-Zone 留給想要餐廳級分區控溫、也願意花錢的人。再往下 Weber Slate 跟第二台 Blackstone 都維持原位，這週沒什麼變動。我的看法沒變，想要最好的烹飪掌控就買 Camp Chef，想用最少錢買到最大鐵板就拿 Blackstone Omnivore，把精準分區控溫擺第一就升到 Traeger。",
   [{"title": "Camp Chef Gridiron 36 是最好的烹飪鐵板", "body": "整片鐵板維持均勻好控的熱度，抗風跟低溫操作都撐得住，這正是便宜鐵板會崩的地方。這塊靈敏又可靠的鐵板讓 smash burger 跟早餐大餐都煎得對，也讓 Gridiron 穩坐第一。"},
    {"title": "Blackstone Original 36 Omnivore 是性價比預設值", "body": "720 平方吋、四個獨立爐頭、價格約 400 美元，是多數後院該買的第一塊鐵板。評測指出它最低溫偏燙、遇風吃力，這個誠實的差距就是它穩坐第二的原因。"},
    {"title": "Traeger Flatrock 3-Zone 給精準分區控溫", "body": "它提供餐廳級的溫度分區，能在同一片鐵板上同時煎、保溫、加熱。對把多區精準控溫擺第一、也接受加價的人來說，這季它的第三名很扎實。"}])
